{"id":"4865785942","type":"page","subType":"live","subtype":"live","ari":"ari:cloud:confluence:4e3a1a04-13f1-4674-95f6-44812aec1da3:page/4865785942","base64EncodedAri":"YXJpOmNsb3VkOmNvbmZsdWVuY2U6NGUzYTFhMDQtMTNmMS00Njc0LTk1ZjYtNDQ4MTJhZWMxZGEzOmNvbnRlbnQvNDg2NTc4NTk0Mg==","status":"current","title":"Friday Sessions","version":{"by":{"type":"known","accountId":"5f3d2a10ea5e2f003979db69","accountType":"atlassian","email":"","publicName":"Ignacio Jorge","profilePicture":{"path":"/wiki/aa-avatar/5f3d2a10ea5e2f003979db69","width":48,"height":48,"isDefault":false},"displayName":"Ignacio Jorge","isExternalCollaborator":false,"isGuest":false,"locale":"en_US","accountStatus":"active","_expandable":{"operations":"","personalSpace":""},"_links":{"self":"https://qubika.atlassian.net/wiki/rest/api/user?accountId=5f3d2a10ea5e2f003979db69"}},"when":"2026-02-13T00:23:14.630Z","friendlyWhen":"Feb 13, 2026","message":"","number":1,"minorEdit":false,"ncsStepVersion":"7","ncsStepVersionSource":"ncs-ack","confRev":"confluence$content$4865785942.12","contentTypeModified":false,"_expandable":{"collaborators":"","content":"/rest/api/content/4865785942"},"_links":{"self":"https://qubika.atlassian.net/wiki/rest/api/content/4865785942/version/1"}},"ancestors":[{"id":"2178416778","type":"page","ari":"ari:cloud:confluence:4e3a1a04-13f1-4674-95f6-44812aec1da3:page/2178416778","base64EncodedAri":"YXJpOmNsb3VkOmNvbmZsdWVuY2U6NGUzYTFhMDQtMTNmMS00Njc0LTk1ZjYtNDQ4MTJhZWMxZGEzOmNvbnRlbnQvMjE3ODQxNjc3OA==","status":"current","title":"Bancard","macroRenderedOutput":{},"extensions":{"position":878},"_expandable":{"container":"/rest/api/space/BAN","metadata":"","restrictions":"/rest/api/content/2178416778/restriction/byOperation","history":"/rest/api/content/2178416778/history","body":"","version":"","descendants":"/rest/api/content/2178416778/descendant","space":"/rest/api/space/BAN","childTypes":"","schedulePublishInfo":"","operations":"","schedulePublishDate":"","children":"/rest/api/content/2178416778/child","ancestors":"","draftVersion":""},"_links":{"self":"https://qubika.atlassian.net/wiki/rest/api/content/2178416778","tinyui":"/x/igDYgQ","editui":"/pages/resumedraft.action?draftId=2178416778","webui":"/spaces/BAN/overview","edituiv2":"/spaces/BAN/pages/edit-v2/2178416778"}}],"macroRenderedOutput":{},"body":{"storage":{"value":"<h1 local-id=\"e4611d4e8ca5\">\uD83D\uDCD8 Friday Session &ndash; Reglas de Funcionamiento</h1><hr local-id=\"55f9b54f-7d88-4234-a083-f7a9b107739f\" /><h2 local-id=\"21555c555a1b\">1️⃣ Prop&oacute;sito del espacio</h2><p local-id=\"6cb471f5394e\">Friday Session es un espacio semanal del equipo para:</p><ul local-id=\"dc10a9ac-b70d-43ec-967d-69293c8974d4\"><li local-id=\"afccf25a-535f-4eb8-b69c-175e1cf4a9a8\"><p local-id=\"c89e935050d6\">Aprender juntos</p></li><li local-id=\"bb40e80d-b336-4820-b7b5-a97798cd4762\"><p local-id=\"ad0892587ccc\">Compartir conocimiento del sistema</p></li><li local-id=\"56e32a30-631c-4da8-ae64-2ea10fa18f47\"><p local-id=\"62dc0d46a044\">Mejorar nuestras pr&aacute;cticas t&eacute;cnicas</p></li><li local-id=\"05ba876e-fd61-47b9-bc61-7fc66d0e4ca6\"><p local-id=\"967e90f0a281\">Pensar arquitectura y dise&ntilde;o</p></li><li local-id=\"32b96e46-87de-4fe3-bc49-8938cdde3194\"><p local-id=\"88c60f08446f\">Fortalecer v&iacute;nculos y cultura t&eacute;cnica</p></li></ul><p local-id=\"6818bed048f2\">No es:</p><ul local-id=\"4f822687-fed2-4c1f-93f7-c91eca9121de\"><li local-id=\"b1065bba-d053-4d93-9c7e-c67853038d96\"><p local-id=\"32c7cbb94d8e\">Una reuni&oacute;n de status</p></li><li local-id=\"bffa5b90-13ac-4fc3-86d3-854c14146d18\"><p local-id=\"b6beba9913b9\">Una retro formal</p></li><li local-id=\"de421e20-9f00-44ba-8df8-04c178f45fe3\"><p local-id=\"a4427e2555a0\">Un espacio para resolver urgencias operativas (o si pero en excepciones muy puntuales)</p></li></ul><hr local-id=\"c6724289-b185-49ea-8f8d-2f67b15a8349\" /><h2 local-id=\"d8c841a64af9\">2️⃣ Frecuencia y duraci&oacute;n</h2><ul local-id=\"2095b6db-2726-42ce-8089-ee9ce7b6867f\"><li local-id=\"1bb93ca6-a822-472a-8fa4-44e1a7ca9275\"><p local-id=\"7a5e91962f52\">Frecuencia: semanal</p></li><li local-id=\"cd40734d-5be2-4145-8731-fbdeffcdabc9\"><p local-id=\"73767c049365\">Duraci&oacute;n: 60 minutos</p></li><li local-id=\"64832fd2-be71-4def-9233-33598739fed2\"><p local-id=\"c79231bb6fe0\">Inicio y cierre puntual</p></li><li local-id=\"ed5563ee-4d53-4d96-aee4-88e8e7346808\"><p local-id=\"f6f081ff5bc9\">Si el contenido termina antes, se libera el espacio</p></li></ul><hr local-id=\"2e488756-d45e-4cab-a889-f49529d39e66\" /><h2 local-id=\"10e3e0b22fb6\">3️⃣ Asistencia y cultura</h2><ul local-id=\"591ab1e4-b8ee-4c31-818e-5497e15b426e\"><li local-id=\"5284d53d-59a3-4e6e-a43c-cf607cb566ca\"><p local-id=\"ad035d2b57ad\">La asistencia es <strong>culturalmente obligatoria</strong>.</p></li><li local-id=\"149bda18-1273-4722-af9c-928f3e3a68a5\"><p local-id=\"35d941f357ab\">Se fomenta fuertemente la c&aacute;mara prendida.</p></li><li local-id=\"fc76d2e5-4b44-4fca-a72c-3013ebb51fb0\"><p local-id=\"a85e2522eb79\">Se espera participaci&oacute;n activa.</p></li></ul><p local-id=\"facf17e87b97\">La Friday Session no es un espacio pasivo.</p><hr local-id=\"6a177fdf-1e53-4e90-b09f-a8975ae0f39b\" /><h2 local-id=\"686cec2c76a6\">4️⃣ Formatos posibles</h2><ul local-id=\"59bca44d-ad8e-4d36-9a74-2d2459ba8840\"><li local-id=\"f04c4aaa-5bc2-4785-9baa-550ff485a2c8\"><p local-id=\"d288bf5c924a\">\uD83D\uDC1B Random Bug Resolution</p></li><li local-id=\"76d0538e-0e89-47cf-a211-0ab50f7c7432\"><p local-id=\"d71bd0f72e04\">\uD83D\uDDFA Team Knowledge Map</p></li><li local-id=\"56c2c014-0875-4f5c-974c-32d5b3ef27db\"><p local-id=\"65729a8e2dc2\">\uD83C\uDFD7 Rails Pattern</p></li><li local-id=\"7a399246-cb24-4c58-8a57-4853ea49ab39\"><p local-id=\"eba00256cda3\">\uD83D\uDD27 Live Refactor Session</p></li><li local-id=\"df9fdad4-da8b-43ab-bb2e-227b691a617e\"><p local-id=\"2c8f785e7c93\">☕ Architecture Coffee</p></li><li local-id=\"34d7c34b-bf74-4ecf-8bfd-8386f9c6119e\"><p local-id=\"6c44342ac857\">\uD83D\uDEE0 Tool Swap</p></li><li local-id=\"1aa38a02-ab12-4667-baca-1deee19ab2a3\"><p local-id=\"02865d8b306f\">\uD83C\uDFAD Tech Debate</p></li><li local-id=\"857a20b4-6dd9-493e-844f-76fcd70c945e\"><p local-id=\"d14f9ebbb03f\">\uD83C\uDFA4 Guest Friday</p></li><li local-id=\"b0b5583a-6ce1-4ad9-8597-7267e089e7d6\"><p local-id=\"240d47a2c6ab\">\uD83C\uDFAE Friday Challenge</p></li><li local-id=\"1598c2d0-fc19-4944-88f3-e2db5ccda004\"><p local-id=\"df2076aeaacf\">\uD83D\uDCF0 Tech News</p></li></ul><p local-id=\"1a9bd2ab9e52\">Cada formato tiene distinto nivel de preparaci&oacute;n.</p><hr local-id=\"4745dbac-6bdc-4075-9e59-33df11cef25a\" /><h2 local-id=\"ab8ed70ec8a7\">5️⃣ Nivel de preparaci&oacute;n esperado</h2><p local-id=\"31520eea3fad\">Se definen tres niveles para balancear carga y profundidad.</p><hr local-id=\"1ba6b614-ea64-4284-9f22-19ec9f42827b\" /><h3 local-id=\"95ea1343ab1f\">\uD83D\uDD39 Bajo (20&ndash;30 minutos de preparaci&oacute;n)</h3><ul local-id=\"036dc143-0f2e-410d-94f4-b911c6702455\"><li local-id=\"e6fc8dd7-c71a-4366-b4ae-75db9e56356b\"><p local-id=\"8dd03e9f7365\">\uD83D\uDEE0 Tool Swap</p></li><li local-id=\"c47fc3f9-e682-4c3a-a95e-0edffd92e494\"><p local-id=\"6596d5ed842d\">\uD83D\uDCF0 Tech News</p></li><li local-id=\"9e2bb530-6064-4bd0-9be7-4c10ca4b049b\"><p local-id=\"1971b44e36cb\">☕ Architecture Coffee (cuando es disparador simple sin material formal)</p></li></ul><hr local-id=\"3b5b2a55-e995-49dc-b5c2-ae591151bccd\" /><h3 local-id=\"1208673f663d\">\uD83D\uDD39 Medio (30&ndash;60 minutos de preparaci&oacute;n)</h3><ul local-id=\"9b8f0671-e16b-4166-a039-9ae85769fac6\"><li local-id=\"87f66543-5e8b-4705-9597-7360598e562c\"><p local-id=\"7798d3b7fbb4\">\uD83D\uDC1B Random Bug Resolution</p></li><li local-id=\"b319dd9e-346f-4a29-b930-4e3f47f89378\"><p local-id=\"49e57db889d8\">\uD83D\uDD27 Live Refactor Session</p></li><li local-id=\"73fcc8a6-9a7e-4776-a50e-cc240b029be5\"><p local-id=\"a4a510e9d63e\">\uD83C\uDFAD Tech Debate</p></li><li local-id=\"36718d34-3c20-4bc5-8d3d-1732ea57be7c\"><p local-id=\"f82574dd0c1f\">☕ Architecture Coffee (cuando requiere contexto m&aacute;s trabajado)</p></li></ul><hr local-id=\"ee090e80-cd66-4757-87d9-5584ca76cfb3\" /><h3 local-id=\"1827d3a5686c\">\uD83D\uDD39 Alto (60&ndash;120 minutos de preparaci&oacute;n)</h3><ul local-id=\"dfd0ee24-6bad-4dd9-ac1b-0b19b7ca26f7\"><li local-id=\"9b5ffc2e-3cbc-4256-a7d3-596a24e2f61e\"><p local-id=\"efcb37e753ce\">\uD83D\uDDFA Team Knowledge Map</p></li><li local-id=\"cc2a2711-9b71-45eb-83c8-f977033b01d1\"><p local-id=\"9c5bd49cead6\">\uD83C\uDFD7 Rails Pattern</p></li><li local-id=\"5d6daecd-9ffc-4953-8677-9ef15ded6ce6\"><p local-id=\"b7d7c381309f\">\uD83C\uDFAE Friday Challenge</p></li><li local-id=\"b8245172-0cbc-45ab-bac7-8b998349bc81\"><p local-id=\"8ce2befd0e0b\">\uD83C\uDFA4 Guest Friday</p></li></ul><p local-id=\"e7e1928da75f\">⚠️ Importante:</p><p local-id=\"8d85857d895f\">No todas las sesiones requieren PPT. En la mayor&iacute;a alcanza con c&oacute;digo, ejemplos, preguntas bien estructuradas o material simple.</p><hr local-id=\"87ccff70-4db4-40aa-b7f6-7ad96aec6f4c\" /><h2 local-id=\"38da76216335\">6️⃣ Asignaci&oacute;n y rotaci&oacute;n</h2><ul local-id=\"fc2091ad-2948-4b9f-8cbc-0cf3100c2921\"><li local-id=\"9f0be9ed-e1c0-4735-9b0a-6a8cd15fa7b1\"><p local-id=\"c54662df934f\">La coordinaci&oacute;n general la lleva Tech Core.</p></li><li local-id=\"4f43b18c-3a04-49d7-9a16-f2eca810ff8c\"><p local-id=\"60d3f9ecb332\">Se asignan responsables con anticipaci&oacute;n.</p></li><li local-id=\"b0951286-119c-4d9e-b88f-7d8512d2f43a\"><p local-id=\"df6dc855fd14\">Se busca equilibrio en la rotaci&oacute;n.</p></li><li local-id=\"0bab24c5-1225-4a9d-9a02-c22602f4fd11\"><p local-id=\"33ce6bb90c78\">Si alguien est&aacute; sobrecargado, puede intercambiar turno.</p></li></ul><p local-id=\"6fbfa5b38d87\">Las sesiones pueden tener:</p><ul local-id=\"030a5093-1059-4023-9e28-c3199104826c\"><li local-id=\"9fcc2c3b-3934-4190-bdcd-97d9503d5dea\"><p local-id=\"cd1fec360062\">Responsable asignado (facilitador formal)</p></li><li local-id=\"2a0b3075-3d07-4eb1-93ae-997ff6ec445c\"><p local-id=\"a3fd82b029bf\">Formato m&aacute;s org&aacute;nico (cuando aplica)</p></li></ul><hr local-id=\"82fe9e29-91e0-498b-aa43-2f6bdb928b81\" /><h2 local-id=\"22784ea91fe1\">7️⃣ Due&ntilde;o de la sesi&oacute;n</h2><p local-id=\"6b2aeba09b92\">Cuando hay responsable asignado:</p><ul local-id=\"04233d87-8c97-4537-b4f0-f9413d21928b\"><li local-id=\"9b7aa4e4-7cf8-42e4-9734-9d0bffa5af5b\"><p local-id=\"791db16dd7cb\">Act&uacute;a como facilitador.</p></li><li local-id=\"67d0d26d-5335-430b-bce8-e6d2839efde2\"><p local-id=\"18959928e682\">Maneja tiempos.</p></li><li local-id=\"ef5633fb-f7dd-447f-a904-d95066f524db\"><p local-id=\"0956e60b94e4\">Modera participaci&oacute;n.</p></li><li local-id=\"9386468b-51f5-4101-bb4d-12db8f72f05a\"><p local-id=\"19d2543799f3\">Cierra con breve resumen final (1&ndash;2 minutos).</p></li></ul><p local-id=\"0ad646319491\">Si no hay responsable asignado:</p><ul local-id=\"b2bac9e7-b562-40ad-bf94-8f2c3aae1dc9\"><li local-id=\"bceafae6-e73e-4abb-a9a8-ddac92cc917e\"><p local-id=\"d3ac3ded5dfe\">La conversaci&oacute;n es m&aacute;s org&aacute;nica.</p></li><li local-id=\"91f6dd42-fc0e-4e2e-a409-c5a764014675\"><p local-id=\"f87d7512493f\">Alguien designado puede moderar si es necesario.</p></li></ul><hr local-id=\"b858c454-7ef9-4a00-8148-b1a4946335ac\" /><h2 local-id=\"2cda4af1ed7b\">8️⃣ Din&aacute;mica de participaci&oacute;n</h2><p local-id=\"d4ce1853d128\">Para evitar pasividad:</p><h3 local-id=\"d5f656b3ad1d\">\uD83D\uDD38 L&iacute;mite de exposici&oacute;n</h3><p local-id=\"e8b232da41bd\">Ning&uacute;n bloque de exposici&oacute;n deber&iacute;a superar los <strong>30&ndash;35 minutos</strong> sin interacci&oacute;n.</p><h3 local-id=\"b6e82cda96c0\">\uD83D\uDD38 Ronda &ldquo;obligatoria&rdquo; (Debates y Architecture Coffee)</h3><p local-id=\"f13059127536\">En estos formatos:</p><ul local-id=\"523b336b-7005-45cd-bb5b-e9d92f56e957\"><li local-id=\"e665fdfc-8b68-41fd-9a69-d33eec5de8bb\"><p local-id=\"17029eb730ae\">Se realiza una ronda donde cada persona debe intervenir al menos una vez (aunque sea muy brevemente).</p></li></ul><h3 local-id=\"0aad04d1aefd\">\uD83D\uDD38 Preguntas dirigidas</h3><p local-id=\"1f80df122c4a\">El facilitador puede invitar participaci&oacute;n directa:</p><blockquote local-id=\"92a27ad3-2a17-4851-8a66-483e38a905cd\"><p local-id=\"f1e3274fec46\">&ldquo;&iquest;C&oacute;mo lo har&iacute;as vos?&rdquo;</p><p local-id=\"e83faac1b4dc\">&ldquo;&iquest;Qu&eacute; riesgo ves ac&aacute;?&rdquo;</p></blockquote><p local-id=\"7302a8a5779c\">La intenci&oacute;n es distribuir la voz, no incomodar.</p><h3 local-id=\"52fde23316e3\">\uD83D\uDD38 Hip&oacute;tesis antes de soluci&oacute;n</h3><p local-id=\"a3a7210061bb\">En sesiones pr&aacute;cticas (Bug, Refactor):</p><ul local-id=\"f68b5bce-3733-4478-b123-320b5fb85a70\"><li local-id=\"941db64b-03b7-4a58-94af-b35172547093\"><p local-id=\"f091e04abda3\">Se discuten hip&oacute;tesis antes de mostrar la soluci&oacute;n (si ya se tiene preparada).</p></li></ul><p local-id=\"eafa96d1eb46\">El objetivo es que no participen siempre los mismos.</p><hr local-id=\"26132b47-991c-4bc4-b823-b90aedd2e2cc\" /><h2 local-id=\"dc2f90b3e6ab\">9️⃣ Impacto en decisiones t&eacute;cnicas</h2><p local-id=\"e614221798e4\">Dependiendo del formato, la sesi&oacute;n puede:</p><ul local-id=\"6fc783da-7fdb-4cd9-a84d-46c1afb2ddc5\"><li local-id=\"ac612127-2cec-40bf-b53c-e0224571912d\"><p local-id=\"0a6854ca3884\">Ser exploratoria.</p></li><li local-id=\"e06dfbce-6138-4674-8f0e-1ed8ad6fd011\"><p local-id=\"5b26b4533c53\">Derivar en un guideline interno.</p></li><li local-id=\"dcddf76b-de0c-43cb-b745-0a4b6a79ecc5\"><p local-id=\"117487bf7185\">Generar una acci&oacute;n concreta.</p></li></ul><p local-id=\"f5cbf6c53c54\">Si surge una conclusi&oacute;n relevante:</p><ul local-id=\"59535e45-928d-4aa8-942b-14c082ebff57\"><li local-id=\"a16a9095-bc10-4096-94d2-9895f3e4d1b0\"><p local-id=\"46a30807ae1e\">Se sugiere documentar brevemente.</p></li><li local-id=\"c183615f-28b2-44da-9cf0-233ea10a226f\"><p local-id=\"998cc401096e\">Se define si requiere seguimiento y el responsable de ese seguimiento.</p></li></ul><hr local-id=\"84ad0adb-221b-4e6f-a536-4e781ab57110\" /><h2 local-id=\"806b15e945c7\">\uD83D\uDD1F Cancelaciones</h2><p local-id=\"ccf5c4e27ed8\">La sesi&oacute;n solo se cancela si:</p><ul local-id=\"34c54e25-9ec9-4048-a7b8-8c23ae7a462f\"><li local-id=\"eb056f4c-3862-43a2-ae6e-f8c84e2e7e40\"><p local-id=\"b2a2a3369a30\">Hay una urgencia cr&iacute;tica real.</p></li><li local-id=\"83288e03-66df-4a45-ba3f-ab7df8259790\"><p local-id=\"6d7420f88be7\">No hay responsable asignado y no se puede reorganizar.</p></li></ul><p local-id=\"0bf57c533cc8\">El objetivo es sostener el espacio en el tiempo.</p><p local-id=\"0e443a6a124a\" />","representation":"storage","embeddedContent":[],"_expandable":{"content":"/rest/api/content/4865785942"}},"_expandable":{"editor":"","atlas_doc_format":"","view":"","export_view":"","styled_view":"","dynamic":"","editor2":"","anonymous_export_view":""}},"extensions":{"position":709},"_expandable":{"childTypes":"","container":"/rest/api/space/BAN","schedulePublishInfo":"","metadata":"","operations":"","schedulePublishDate":"","children":"/rest/api/content/4865785942/child","restrictions":"/rest/api/content/4865785942/restriction/byOperation","history":"/rest/api/content/4865785942/history","draftVersion":"","descendants":"/rest/api/content/4865785942/descendant","space":"/rest/api/space/BAN"},"_links":{"editui":"/spaces/BAN/pages/4865785942/Friday+Sessions","webui":"/spaces/BAN/pages/4865785942/Friday+Sessions","edituiv2":"/spaces/BAN/pages/4865785942/Friday+Sessions","context":"/wiki","self":"https://qubika.atlassian.net/wiki/rest/api/content/4865785942","tinyui":"/x/VgAGIgE","collection":"/rest/api/content","base":"https://qubika.atlassian.net/wiki"}}